    <briefdescription>
<para>Main application controller managing screen, input, and modal overlays. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="classevab_1_1_boxy" kindref="compound">Boxy</ref> is a singleton that provides global access to the display system, manages the current screen, and handles modal popups. </para>
